Package ut.twente.notebridge.model

Class BaseUser

java.lang.Object
ut.twente.notebridge.model.BaseEntity
ut.twente.notebridge.model.BaseUser
Direct Known Subclasses:
Person, Sponsor
public class BaseUser extends BaseEntity
This class represents a base user in the application. Since username, email, password, phoneNumber, picture, description are common fields in all users, they are defined here Other user classes extend this class
